title: Choosing Life: Confessions of a Planned Parenthood Director - Abby Johnson
description:
Abby Johnson thought she was helping women as a director of a Planned Parenthood. Meeting monthly abortion quotas, targeting minority communities, telling women to deceive their families - she believed all of this was in the best interest of women. . . until the day she witnessed an abortion first hand.
